<h1><em>PLOS Pathogens</em> Article Type Descriptions</h1>

<a name="opinion" id="opinion"></a>
<h2>Opinion</h2>
<p>Opinion articles provide a forum for expression of views, and responses
to previous statements, on a range of topical, emerging and
controversial issues.</p>

<a name="pearls" id="pearls"></a>
<h2>Pearls</h2>
<p>Pearls provide concise, practical and educational insights into
topics that span the pathogens field.</p>


<a name="review" id="review"></a>
<h2>Review</h2>
<p>Review articles synthesize the best available evidence on a topic
relevant to the pathogens community.</p>

